Adding a new theorem to Mathlib/Algebra/Order/Floor.lean : 

```
theorem round_half_bot : a - (1 / 2 : â„š) < round a := by
  rw [round_eq, show (a - 1 / 2 : â„š) = (a + 1 / 2) - 1 by ring]
  exact Int.sub_one_lt_floor (a + 1 / 2)
```
